    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_3_758-808",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "758-808",
      "markText": "隋唐之制度虽极广博纷复，然究析其因素，不出三源：一曰（北）魏、（北）齐，二曰梁、陈，三曰（西）魏、周",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=758&rangeEnd=808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=758&rangeEnd=808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_13_12696-12787",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "12696-12787",
      "markText": "寅恪按：瑛乃玄宗初立之太子，其皇位继承既已不能固定矣，至于此后所立之太子即后来继位之肃宗，其皇位继承权亦屡经动摇，若非乘安禄山叛乱之际拥兵自立为帝，则其果能终嗣皇位与否，殊未可知也。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=12696&rangeEnd=12787",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=12696&rangeEnd=12787"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_3_987-1032",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "987-1032",
      "markText": "又西晋永嘉之乱，中原魏晋以降之文化转移保存于凉州一隅，至北魏取凉州，而河西文化遂输入于魏。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=987&rangeEnd=1032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=987&rangeEnd=1032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_4_579-615",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "579-615",
      "markText": "由三代而上，治出于一，而礼乐达于天下；由三代而下，治出于二，而礼乐为虚名",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=579&rangeEnd=615",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=579&rangeEnd=615"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_3_1252-1352",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1252-1352",
      "markText": "所谓（西）魏、周之源者，凡西魏、北周之创作有异于山东及江左之旧制，或阴为六镇鲜卑之野俗，或远承魏、（西）晋之遗风，若就地域言之，乃关陇区内保存之旧时汉族文化，所适应鲜卑六镇势力之环境，而产生之混合品。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1252&rangeEnd=1352",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1252&rangeEnd=1352"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_4_28249-28305",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "28249-28305",
      "markText": "自晋室南渡之后，过江名士尚能沿述西朝旧说，而中原旧壤久已不闻此论，斯又河西一隅之地尚能保存典午中朝遗说之一证也。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=28249&rangeEnd=28305",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=28249&rangeEnd=28305"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_4_757-795",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "757-795",
      "markText": "然用之郊庙朝廷，自搢绅大夫从事其间者皆莫能晓习，而天下之人至于老死未尝见也。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=795",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=795"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_4_27123-27163",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "27123-27163",
      "markText": "永嘉之乱，中州之人士避地河西，张氏礼而用之。子孙相承，衣冠不坠，故凉州号为多士。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=27123&rangeEnd=27163",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=27123&rangeEnd=27163"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_4_30507-30569",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "30507-30569",
      "markText": "东西两国俱以六镇流民创业，初自表面观察，可谓魏孝文迁都洛阳以后之汉化政策遭一大打击，而逆转为胡化，诚北朝政治社会之一大变也。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=30507&rangeEnd=30569",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=30507&rangeEnd=30569"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_6_941-1026",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "941-1026",
      "markText": "司马氏以东汉末年之儒学大族创建晋室，统制中国，其所制定之刑律尤为儒家化，既为南朝历代所因袭，北魏改律，复采用之，辗转嬗蜕，经由（北）齐隋，以至于唐，实为华夏刑律不祧之正统",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=941&rangeEnd=1026",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=941&rangeEnd=1026"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_13_43755-43808",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "43755-43808",
      "markText": "元和朝虽号称中兴，然外朝士大夫之党派既起，内廷阉寺党派之竞争亦剧，遂至牵涉皇位继承问题，而宪宗因以被弑矣。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=43755&rangeEnd=43808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=43755&rangeEnd=43808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_14_24177-24190",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "24177-24190",
      "markText": "唐亡于黄巢，而祸基于桂林。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=24177&rangeEnd=24190",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=24177&rangeEnd=24190"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_3_457-512",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "457-512",
      "markText": "李唐传世将三百年，而杨隋享国为日至短，两朝之典章制度传授因袭几无不同，故可视为一体，并举合论，此不待烦言而解者",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=457&rangeEnd=512",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=457&rangeEnd=512"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_13_16972-17016",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "16972-17016",
      "markText": "所谓士族者，其初并不专用其先代之高官厚禄为其唯一之表征，而实以家学及礼法等标异于其他诸姓",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=16972&rangeEnd=17016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=16972&rangeEnd=17016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_12_27434-27503",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "27434-27503",
      "markText": "至泉献诚为盖苏文之孙，男生之子，亡国败降之余裔，其武伎精妙犹称当时第一，则高丽之以东隅小国能屡抗隋唐全盛之日倾国之师，岂无故哉！岂无故哉！",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=27434&rangeEnd=27503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=27434&rangeEnd=27503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_13_17129-17182",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "17129-17182",
      "markText": "卢玄绪业著闻，首应旌命，子孙继迹，为世盛门。其文武功业殆无足纪，而见重于时，声高冠带，盖德业儒素有过人者。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=17129&rangeEnd=17182",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=17129&rangeEnd=17182"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_13_51296-51364",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "51296-51364",
      "markText": "是时训、注之权赫于天下，既得行其志，生平恩雠丝毫必报。因杨虞卿之狱挟忌李宗闵、李德裕。心所恶者，目为二人之党，朝士相继斥逐，班列为之一空",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36235886&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=51296&rangeEnd=51364",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/336329b07228ea6e336adce?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=51296&rangeEnd=51364"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36235886_13_62483-62524",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "62483-62524",
